column5: Go back in time as you enter this tastefully furnished home . 1800 era Victorian furniture and hardwood floors lead you out to a screened veranda where you can entertain your guests with a BBQ. You will also find a fully equipped gourmet kitchen, family room with free WiFi, DVDs, Netflix, games, a formal living room and dining room with antique dishes.
column8: A Charming Victorian Bed and Breakfast
